#Key Next         A       SCM     Next [*] Focus
#Key Prior        A       SCM     Prev [*] Focus
#Key Tab	A	A	SCM	Next [*] Focus
#Key Super_L	A	SCM	Prev [*] Focus

# Alt-Tab goodness or else we'd go insane
